title: Person In Manual Wheelchair Medium Dark Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Wheelchair User Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: A person using a manual wheelchair, depicted with a medium-dark skin tone. This emoji represents mobility, accessibility, and individuals who use wheelchairs for transportation.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the person in a manual wheelchair with a medium-dark skin tone is depicted with dignity and clear representation. The wheelchair itself is rendered with subtle shading and smooth contours, emphasizing its functional design, while the person's posture conveys a sense of active engagement and mobility. This emoji, a hallmark of Apple's inclusive design, is a powerful symbol of accessibility, independence, and diverse human experiences.
